<div class='container'>
  <br/>
  <div class="progress">
    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="20" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 25%;">
      <span>1. 帐号注册</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="20" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 25%;">
      <span>2. 用户激活</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-success" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="20" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 25%;">
      <span>3. 绑定银行信息</span>
    </div>
    <div class="progress-bar" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="20" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: 25%;">
      <span>4. 注册成功</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <h3>完成注册</h3>
  <hr/>
  <form role='form' action="/user/update/<%= user_info.id %>" method="POST" class="form-horizontal">
    <% if (flash && flash.err) { %>
    <div class="alert alert-danger">					
      <% Object.keys(flash.err).forEach(function(error) { %>
      <%= error %>: <%= JSON.stringify(flash.err[error]) %>
      <% }) %>
    </div>
    <% } %>
    <div class="alert alert-success">
      <p class='text-center'>
        恭喜您，你已经完成注册，您需要在用户主页继续完善个人信息以便使用本站所有功能。点击确定按钮回到用户主页。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-2 col-md-offset-10">
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block haha-btn-toggle" onclick="handle_submit_btn(this)">确定</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <input class='hidden' name='_csrf' value='<%= _csrf %>' />
    <input class='hidden' name='reg_completed' value='true' />
  </form>
</div>
